      "name": "ASTM F1717 compression-bending operating envelope",
      "description": "Axial compressive load range 0–2500 N; applied bending moment 0–25 N·m; crosshead displacement rate 5 mm/min ± 0.5 mm/min; ambient temperature 20–25 °C; construct geometry tolerances ±0.05 mm on screw outer diameter (7.5 mm nominal) and ±0.1 mm on rod diameter (5.5 mm nominal); polyethylene block fixture per ASTM F1717 Section 7. Validation experiments sampled boundary points at 500 N and 2400 N axial load with bending moments of 2 N·m and 23 N·m, confirming model fidelity across the declared envelope."
    },
    "hasApplicabilityConstraint": {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/cou/cou1-noncannulated/applicability",
