      "name": "Non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw, static loading only",
      "description": "Applicable exclusively to non-cannulated pedicle screws with nominal outer diameter 7.5 mm ± 0.05 mm tested under quasi-static (monotonic) compression-bending per ASTM F1717. Excludes cannulated variants, dynamic fatigue loading, screws with outer diameter outside 7.40–7.55 mm, and constructs assembled with rods other than 5.5 mm cobalt-chrome or titanium alloy. In-vivo loading conditions and patient-specific bone properties are outside scope."
    }
